OL,6,FA health board has apologise to a
OL,7,Fgrieving family after it emerged that
OL,8,Fa hospital had released the wrong body
OL,9,Ffor them to bury.
OL,11,FThe Aneurin Bevan University Health
OL,12,FBoard said they were "devastated" by
OL,13,Fthe mix-up at The Grange hospital in
OL,14,FCwmbran.
OL,16,FThe family were not notified until
OL,17,Fseveral months after the death and it
OL,18,Fis understood a funeral had already
OL,19,Fbeen held.
